Class TimerConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.hekate.metrics.local.MetricConfigBase<TimerConfig>

  • public class TimerConfig
extends MetricConfigBase<TimerConfig>
    Configuration for TimerMetric.

    Fore more details about timers and other metrics please see the documentation of LocalMetricsService.

    See Also:
    LocalMetricsServiceFactory.withMetric(MetricConfigBase), LocalMetricsService.register(TimerConfig)

      • setRateName

        public void setRateName(String rateName)
        Sets the name of a metric that will hold the rate value of this timer. Can contain only alpha-numeric characters and non-repeatable dots/hyphens.

        This parameter is optional. If specified then an additional metric of that name will be registered within the LocalMetricsService and will hold the rate value of this timer.

        Parameters:
        rateName - Name of a metric that will hols the rate value of this timer (can contain only alpha-numeric characters and non-repeatable dots/hyphens).
